snippet.title: Them's Fightin' Herds - Stronghoof Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Stronghoof the Reindeer, the second DLC character in the Season 1 Pass, available now!

Them’s Fightin’ Herds is available on PlayStation 4 & 5, Xbox One & Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and Steam.

Buy TFH: https://mane6.com/buy
